nodes.text: This RA-7 protocol droid was seen on Coruscant around 21 BBY during the Clone Wars.

This protocol droid, along with an astromech droid, could be found in a dark alley in the planet Coruscant's lower market districts. When the Assassin droid HELIOS-3D and Todo 360 were pursuing R2-D2 under orders from Cad Bane, HELIOS-3D accidentally stunned the astromech droid, confusing it with R2. This droid noticed the attack and started running away.
